Package: fgczQuartoTemplate
Title: FGCZ Quarto Report Templates and Shared Styling
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Peter", "Leary", role = "aut"),
    person("Jonas", "Grossmann", role = "aut"),
    person("Falko", "Noé", role = "aut"),
    person("Witold", "Wolski", , "witold@ethz.ch", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Shared FGCZ Quarto styling and report templates with
    configurable tab colours and numbering, searchable figures and tables,
    and downloadable plots, source files, and standalone HTML reports.
    Includes helpers to stage the shared assets beside a .qmd file and render
    it.
